		<div id="comment_body_64177549">I mean, it was not hard to predict that "long charging times" mean "long queues / wait times" at public chargers, and many have predicted this to happen.<br>The possible solutions are obvious: Either make charging so quick that it only takes few minutes to fill a battery, or make public charging so expensive that people will either avoid doing it at all or pay so much that this finances more and more charging stations until the demand is met.</div>
